gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString:
This layer represents the spatial extent of Base Blueprint 2022. It reflects the exterior boundary of the [Base Blueprint 2022 subregions](https://secas-fws.hub.arcgis.com/datasets/79299d5e9e094e6bafa71896f24ece8d/about).
Code used to create this layer is available in the [Southeast Blueprint 2022 Data Download](https://www.sciencebase.gov/catalog/file/get/62d57290d34e87fffb2dda52?name=Southeast_Blueprint_2022_Data_Download.zip) under BlueprintInputs > BaseBlueprint2022 > 6_Code. The final step of the code used to create the subregions exports the extent layer.

gmd:purpose.gco:CharacterString: This layer represents the spatial extent of Base Blueprint 2022.
